code: @Test public void testRssHttpNoCamelParameters() throws Exception {     RssEndpoint rss = context.getEndpoint("rss://http://www.iafrica.com/pls/cms/grapevine.xml?sortEntries=true&feedHeader=true", RssEndpoint.class).     assertNotNull(rss).     assertEquals("http://www.iafrica.com/pls/cms/grapevine.xml", rss.getFeedUri()).     assertEquals(true, rss.isFeedHeader()).     assertEquals(true, rss.isSortEntries()). }

@Test public void testRssHttpNoCamelParametersAndOneFeedParameter() throws Exception {     RssEndpoint rss = context.getEndpoint("rss://http://www.iafrica.com/pls/cms/grapevine.xml?sortEntries=true&feedHeader=true&foo=bar", RssEndpoint.class).     assertNotNull(rss).     assertEquals("http://www.iafrica.com/pls/cms/grapevine.xml?foo=bar", rss.getFeedUri()).     assertEquals(true, rss.isFeedHeader()).     assertEquals(true, rss.isSortEntries()). }
